#: ../../source/api/app.md:3
msgid ""
"`App` manages the pygame window and the active worlds. Most beginner "
"projects do not need to create an `App` directly because `world.run()` "
"starts the default application loop."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/api/app.md:7
msgid ""
"Use `App` only when you intentionally manage more than one world or need "
"direct control over the application lifecycle."
msgstr ""

